== Nearby Bridges == * {{ill|Sumida River|ja|隅田川|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sumida River|qq=}} : (Upstream) - {{ill|Senju Shiomi Bridge|ja|千住汐入大橋|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Senju Shiomi Bridge|qq=}} - {{ill|Suijin Bridge|ja|水神大橋|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Suijin Bridge|qq=}} * '''Shirahige Bridge''' - {{ill|Sakura Bridge (Tokyo)|ja|桜橋 (東京都)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sakura Bridge (Tokyo)|qq=}} - {{ill|Kototoi Bridge|ja|言問橋|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kototoi Bridge|qq=}} - (Downstream) == See Also == * {{ill|Arakawa Under the Bridge|ja|荒川アンダー ザ ブリッジ|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Arakawa Under the Bridge|qq=}} (A manga that features this bridge in several scenes)
